overview: Battling Beauties! Sexy Victims! Countless Deathtraps! Mystery & Adventure! All these and more combine when Fanny Starr, private eye, becomes involved in "The Case of the Kidnapped Heiresses!" But in order to solve the case, Fanny must survive being a human sacrifice, being blown to bits, and being suffocated in a locked coffin!
title: The Misadventures of Fanny Starr
